      &lt;p&gt;Fellow command-line junkies either love &lt;a href=&#34;http://cheat.errtheblog.com/&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34;&gt;the cheat gem&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=&#34;http://ozmm.org/&#34; rel=&#34;external&#34;&gt;Chris Wanstrath&lt;/a&gt; or they&amp;rsquo;ve never heard of it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What &amp;ldquo;cheat&amp;rdquo; offers is a plethora (currently 601) of text-based cheat sheets at the tip of your fingers. Go ahead, give it a try:&lt;/p&gt;
